<b>Proc Level:</b>&nbsp; 50<br>
        <b>Max Damage:</b> 124.3<br>
        <b>Damage/Delay Ratio:</b> Destructive (0.647)<br>
        <b>Max Attack Speed:</b> Very Fast (18.888)<br>
        <b>Weapon Performance:</b> Excellent (11.205)<br>
<b>Effect Details:</b>&nbsp; This is perhaps one of the ultimate Darkness effects.  Delivering 1200 damage in 1 min 36 seconds, and slowing the movement rate of the target up to 65%.<br>
